<div class="evidenceBorder"><h2><i class="mch-compass3"></i> MICRO-LEARNING GOALS</h2>
<p><img src="../../images/new-smart-8.2.jpg" alt="Module icon" class="right border" width="600"/>On this <strong>micro-learning  page</strong> for <strong>Community Expertise and Perspectives</strong>, we start by focusing on <strong>proficiency</strong> &mdash; understanding key concepts &mdash; and them move onto <strong>practice</strong> &mdash; considering how to frame this competency based on what you already know. Through this process, we introduce the basics  by:</p>
